data.description: Beautifully maintained with stunning golf course views!  This 2 bedroom, 2 bath home has a beautiful golf course view of the 14th green.  Updated kitchen with upgraded lighting and. stainless appliances, granite countertops and rich cabinetry! Newer water heater and exterior paint.  Wonderful natural light!  Perfect for entertaining those out of town guests, as bedrooms are on the opposite sides of the home.  Enjoy the wonderful community amenities, which include pickle ball, tennis, basketball, indoor pool and spa, state of the art fitness room, social calendar and more!
